      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose $u_n = \\frac {96\\times(-1)^n}{(2n-3)(2n-1)(2n+1)(2n+3)(2n+5)}$\net $v_n = \\sum_{k=0}^n\\,u_k$.",
        "html": "<p>On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n = \\frac {96\\times(-1)^n}{(2n-3)(2n-1)(2n+1)(2n+3)(2n+5)}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(v_n = \\sum_{k=0}^n\\,u_k\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6d327d31-095e-49dc-9325-57c764e6bdfb",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "{\\'E}tudier les suites $(v_{2n})$ et $(v_{2n+1})$ et\n    montrer que la suite $(v_n)$ est convergente.",
        "html": "<p><span>É</span>tudier les suites <span class=\"math inline\">\\((v_{2n})\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\((v_{2n+1})\\)</span> et montrer que la suite <span class=\"math inline\">\\((v_n)\\)</span> est convergente.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6ae64fcb-91e1-4c4e-89bf-fc266f2ab798",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\ell = \\lim_{n\\to\\infty} v_n$ {\\`a} $10^{-5}$ pr{\\`e}s.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell = \\lim_{n\\to\\infty} v_n\\)</span> <span>à</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(10^{-5}\\)</span> pr<span>è</span>s.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "db82c6d8-54c2-488d-825c-3fc34f7e6433",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\ell = \\pi$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell = \\pi\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
